source:
TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_SEQ_00<tab>Stigma-4 requires a swift pair of legs for an urgent delivery.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>Règle spéciale<var 1D /var>:  synchronisation de quête avec limitation de job ou de classe<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
<var 1A 02 /var>* Il n'est possible de progresser dans cette quête qu'avec la classe qui a servi à la commencer.<var 1A 01 /var>

Stigma-4 aimerait vous confier une livraison.

source: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_TODO_00<tab>Deliver the packed meals to the Karellians patrolling the wellspring of regret.
target: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_TODO_00<tab>Apporter les paniers-repas des Dernières Réminiscences aux soldats près de la source des Velléitaires

source: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_STIGMA4_000_000<tab>Task log indicates pending request for <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>. Karellians patrolling the wellspring of regret require the delivery of sustenance.
target: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_STIGMA4_000_000<tab>Entité alliée <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, j'ai une requête à vous communiquer. Pourriez-vous apporter ces paniers-repas des Dernières Réminiscences à deux soldats en patrouille près de la source des Velléitaires<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_STIGMA4_000_001<tab>Depletion of nutrients in the biological vessel directly correlates to emotional instability, which is statistically proven as the source of psychological warfare, physical altercations, and/or severe grumpiness. Current trajectory classified as “untenable.” Proceed with caution and haste.
target: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_STIGMA4_000_001<tab>Ils manquent tous deux de nutriments. La faim entraîne des sautes d'humeur qui pourraient mettre en péril leur relation. Merci d'effectuer cette tâche le plus rapidement possible.

source: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_KARELEANA04613_000_010<tab>What is it? Make it quick─patrolling requires the utmost concentration, you know.

TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_KARELEANA04613_000_011<tab>Food? For me? Why, how unexpected... Truth be told, my patrols so far have been an exercise in battling off pangs of boredom and hunger in equal measure. This, at least, shall help with the latter.
target: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_KARELEANA04613_000_011<tab>Oh, vous m'avez apporté un panier-repas des Dernières Réminiscences<var 1D /var>? C'est gentil, merci.

source: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_KARELEANA04613_000_012<tab>While you're here, might not you do something about that layabout Freedom Fighter? I've noticed a number of careless errors in his work. If I am expected to work alongside his kind, it is only right that he be held to the same standard of diligence, empty stomach notwithstanding.
target: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_KARELEANA04613_000_012<tab>Je ne sais pas si c'est à cause de la faim, mais le soldat du Front de libération manque de con<var 16 /var>cen<var 16 /var>tra<var 16 /var>tion et n'arrête pas de commettre des erreurs... Je suis sûr qu'il serait plus efficace de le placer sous nos ordres...

source: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_KARELEANA04613_000_013<tab>...Ah, but perhaps it is best not to think about work until after I've eaten this gift. So quickly does one's mood turn dark without sustenance. You have my thanks.
target: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_KARELEANA04613_000_013<tab>Enfin, vous n'êtes pas là pour écouter mes plaintes. Je vais réfléchir une fois le ventre plein et lui donnerai à nouveau mon avis.

source: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_KARELEANB04613_000_015<tab>Oh, it's you. I don't suppose you've come to help me with my work?
TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_KARELEANB04613_000_016<tab>This...this is food! I'm so hungry the rocks and dirt were beginning to look like freshly baked bread and powdered sugar. Thank you for this bounty!
target: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_KARELEANB04613_000_016<tab>Ooh, un panier-repas des Dernières Réminiscences<var 1D /var>! Ça tombe bien, je commençais à avoir un petit creux<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_KARELEANB04613_000_017<tab>Speaking of which, you haven't seen that would-be taskmaster from the Global Community around, have you? He criticizes me upon every opportunity─not a surprise for someone of his stripe, but my ears may well bleed from the abuse...
target: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_KARELEANB04613_000_017<tab>Vous avez déjà parlé au soldat de la Fédération<var 1D /var>? Il arrête pas de donner des ordres et de se prendre pour le chef... Je comprends pas d'où lui vient cette arrogance.

source: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_KARELEANB04613_000_018<tab>...Still, little use wondering why villains will be vile when there's a meal to be had. Now, I feast!
target: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_KARELEANB04613_000_018<tab>Enfin bref, mon ventre a d'autres priorités. Je lui dirai le fond de ma pensée après m'être rempli la panse.

source: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_STIGMA4_000_020<tab>Return of <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var> confirmed. Awaiting detailed report.
target: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_STIGMA4_000_020<tab>Bip... Retour de l'entité alliée confirmé. Merci de m'informer sur la situation.

source: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_STIGMA4_000_021<tab>Relational deterioration between patrolling Karellians acknowledged. <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>'s assistance in this matter evaluated as vital to preserving peace and averting a breakdown of operations.
target: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_STIGMA4_000_021<tab>Leur entente était donc bel et bien menacée. Pourquoi les êtres organiques ne cherchent pas à résoudre ce bogue appelé “émotions”<var 1D /var>? C'est incom<var 16 /var>pré<var 16 /var>hen<var 16 /var>si<var 16 /var>ble.

source: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_STIGMA4_000_022<tab>Why organic life-forms retain the programming error colloquially referred to as “emotions” remains incomprehensible. Even so, a compensatory wage has been prepared for <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>'s monetary and emotional needs. Remember to refuel as necessary.
target: TEXT_BANOMI107_04613_STIGMA4_000_022<tab>Merci pour votre travail, le pire a pu être évité grâce à vous. Veuillez accepter cette récompense.
